Docker_demo_project_QA_Krina

Steps to run using Docker

1) Install docker client on you Mac
2) run the docker compose file in detached mode using "docker-compose -f /path to dcoker file/docker-compose.yml up -d
3) check the containers using docker ps
4) Below containers should be up and running
   selenium/node-opera-debug:latest
   selenium/node-chrome-debug:latest
   selenium/node-firefox-debug:latest
   selenium/node-edge:91.0
   selenium/hub
5) Install VNC client and connect it to any web browser port which you want to connect.